{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150","id":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150","title":"Canada 150 on Parliament Hill","date_modified":"2023-01-02T01:45:01-05:00","date_published":"2017-07-04T23:34:36-04:00","content_html":"<p>I visited Ottawa recently to stay with my aunts and their families, and also to get to Parliament Hill for the Canada 150 concert.</p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- The crowds were pretty thick by Ottawa standards...\">- The crowds were pretty thick by Ottawa standards&hellip;</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/crowd-stop.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd at a Park &amp; Ride\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/crowd-bus.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd in a bus\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- There were stories of immigrants posted downtown.\">- There were stories of immigrants posted downtown.</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/immigrant-stories.jpg\" alt=\"Immigrant Stories\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- A speech by the Prince of Wales was going on while we were walking downtown.\">- A speech by the Prince of Wales was going on while we were walking downtown.</span>\n <span id=\"- There were lots of trained stilt walkers.\">- There were lots of trained stilt walkers.</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/stilt-geometric.jpg\" alt=\"Stilt walker in a geometric costume\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/stilt-bird.jpg\" alt=\"Stilt walker in a bird rider costume\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/stilt-dark-bird.jpg\" alt=\"Another stilt walker in a bird rider costume\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- On Parliament Hill, it was burning hot throughout the afternoon.\">- On Parliament Hill, it was burning hot throughout the afternoon.</span>\n <span id=\"- I stood on the stone fence of the Parliament... until the guards told people to get down.\">- I stood on the stone fence of the Parliament&hellip; until the guards told people to get down.</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/stand-on-fence.jpg\" alt=\"Standing on fence of Parliament\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- The view was ok while it lasted.\">- The view was ok while it lasted.</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/fence-view.jpg\" alt=\"View from the fence\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- Many presenters, even the ones that weren't explicitly anti-colonial, made it a point to mention that Ottawa was built on Algonquin land.\">- Many presenters, even the ones that weren&rsquo;t explicitly anti-colonial, made it a point to mention that Ottawa was built on Algonquin land.</span>\n <span id=\"- SNOW BIRDS: apparently Serena Ryder tours with these jets all the time :D\">- SNOW BIRDS: apparently Serena Ryder tours with these jets all the time :D</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/snow-birds.jpg\" alt=\"Snow Birds\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- Can you identify this flying object?\">- Can you identify this flying object?</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/ufo.jpg\" alt=\"Probably a balloon\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- The rain came fast, but most were prepared.\">- The rain came fast, but most were prepared.</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/rain.jpg\" alt=\"Evening rain\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- There were some *charming* details you'd miss if you saw this on TV.\">- There were some <em>charming</em> details you&rsquo;d miss if you saw this on TV.</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/canada-150/attachments/teleprompt.jpg\" alt=\"Teleprompter\" /></p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- The evening events were delayed for a long time, everyone got drenched. The organizers seeded false hope by starting an announcement every few minutes ... just to tell everyone that events were delayed &quot;due to weather&quot;.\">- The evening events were delayed for a long time, everyone got drenched. The organizers seeded false hope by starting an announcement every few minutes &hellip; just to tell everyone that events were delayed &ldquo;due to weather&rdquo;.</span>\n <span id=\"- A group of ravers on the side of the stage started singing the national anthem a few times while the organizers failed to deliver. It was really touching.\">- A group of ravers on the side of the stage started singing the national anthem a few times while the organizers failed to deliver. It was really touching.</span>\n <span id=\"- They also sang *Hakuna Matata*.\">- They also sang <em>Hakuna Matata</em>.</span>\n <span id=\"- My fam and I left the scene at 21:00 as there was nothing going on, so we didn't get to see Cirque du Soleil or the fireworks.\">- My fam and I left the scene at 21:00 as there was nothing going on, so we didn&rsquo;t get to see Cirque du Soleil or the fireworks.</span></p>","attachments":[{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/crowd-bus.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/crowd-stop.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/fence-view.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/immigrant-stories.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/rain.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/snow-birds.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/stand-on-fence.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/stilt-bird.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/stilt-dark-bird.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/stilt-geometric.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/teleprompt.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"},{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/canada-150/attachments/ufo.jpg","mime_type":"image/jpeg"}],"tags":["biographical"],"_ratan_blog_class":""}
